DIY TAN REMOVING HACK 

Mix 5 tbsp glycerin & 1 tbsp lemon juice in a bottle and apply daily before bed

Benefits-
1. Lemon fades tan with its natural citric acid and Vitamin C, which gently lighten pigmentation and help even out your skin tone.
2. Glycerine keeps your skin hydrated and soothed, preventing dryness and supporting skin healing after sun exposure for a natural glow.
